@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_zmcbtu(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = tmp
    v1 = (wp.cos((tmp + 0.51 - v0 + 0.96)) + v2)
    v0 = (0.97 - ((tmp + 0.93 - v2 + 0.67) / (v1 + 0.78 - v0 + 0.85)))
    data[tid] = v0
